      "content": "but what story is there left? he was the part of me that actually lived. i'm just the leftover shell. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing can happen because the person i was supposed to do everything with is gone. it just feels... wrong. like i'm just taking up space that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
