    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a safe place to rest though. it feels like a void. i look at the empty side of the bed and it's like the universe is telling me i shouldn't even be here. like i'm just a mistake that hasn't been corrected yet. if everything was meant to be together, then why am i still here by myself? it feels like i'm just dragging this heavy, empty thing around for no reason.",
